{"tid":1469695,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[私刑] 數名被捕示威者手腳骨折　送北區醫院拘留治理","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T14:50:06.000Z","uid":2617,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b54ddd4293e5e945f5ec2772f88b27a1b97ca88f","tid":1469695,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:45:33.000Z","msg":"反條例風波未平，周日（11日）多區爆發衝突多人被捕，有指部分被扣留在文錦渡新屋嶺扣留中心，警方被指阻撓律師見被捕人士。網上流傳今日數十名被捕年青人因骨折，被警方押送至北區醫院求診，質疑有人濫用私刑，逼使示威者認罪。<br />\n<br />\n數名示威者手腳骨折<br />\n<br />\n據了解，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大部分送院的示威者頸痛，現時警方在北區醫院看管著數名手腳骨折的示威者</span></span>，他們目前情況穩定，但受警方監控。消息指，目前病房內「警察多過病人」。網傳有被捕人士脊椎受壓，據悉病房內並末有相關個案。此外，示威者可以致電聯絡家人，亦有人協助示威者尋求律師協助。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員林卓廷在fb上表示，已聯絡醫管局，要求全力確保病人權益，並立即跟進及回應市民的關注。<br />\n<br />\n最少9人留醫骨科病房 48小時僅獲准見律師一次<br />\n<br />\n香港01記者今晚前往北區醫院，多名警員出入病房，記者接觸到五名在骨科病房留醫的被捕人士，其中一人右邊頭部受傷，貼有紗布。目前四人已保釋，保釋條件不一，他們表示，病房內共有9名被捕人士，當中一人手骨骨折。他們全部在銅鑼灣被捕，其後被扣留在新屋嶺扣留中心。一名被捕人士指，被捕時曾被警員以警棍打，但扣留時則沒有，然而在新屋嶺期間不准許見律師，送至北區醫院才得見面一次，再要求見律師遭拒。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好人好者點會骨折呀屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"1d3243645997ae9032de71b7ea14e4993a8a648e","tid":1469695,"uid":191275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3661a1418ce9fa8ed2b73e45fc8d430b69cc29","tid":1469695,"uid":95487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:47:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6cf12ef83eaa19bfbb09f16347bc77d67a41f7d","tid":1469695,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:47:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df756c3a95f92959fe7d3607d079da5b0620ac5","tid":1469695,"uid":94836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:47:58.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"72a9f9e58fa4e57abf06ebc96bb65e8d3c5dd375","tid":1469695,"uid":22407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:48:27.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"89494d6124469d548bdece23d4c8e49d82868b86","tid":1469695,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:48:27.000Z","msg":"推呀屌"},{"pid":"24b14e39a47106c4d0bbd798bb6a6ce817fe8e1f","tid":1469695,"uid":35699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再割就玩完<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x